arkus/tutorial/order/OrderApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/resources/static/css/default.css: Moved from resources/css for Spring Boot static serving\n- smoke.py: 7 smoke tests covering all endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/resources/templates/orderTemplate.html: Qute include template (replaced by flat Thymeleaf)\n- src/main/resources/templates/lineItemTemplate.html: Qute include template (replaced by flat Thymeleaf)\n- src/main/resources/css/: Old static asset directory (moved to static/)\n\nUnchanged:\n- All 7 entity classes (use standard jakarta.persistence.* - framework-agnostic)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T01:45:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure: 16 Java files, Quarkus 3.30.5, H2 DB\n[2026-03-17T01:46:00Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 7 test cases\n[2026-03-17T01:47:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml: Quarkus deps -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 starters\n[2026-03-17T01:48:00Z] [info] Migrated application.properties: quarkus.* -> spring.* \n[2026-03-17T01:49:00Z] [info] Created OrderApplication.java Spring Boot entry point\n[2026-03-17T01:50:00Z] [info] Refactored 5 repository classes: CDI -> Spring annotations\n[2026-03-17T01:51:00Z] [info] Refactored OrderConfigService: CDI -> Spring Service\n[2026-03-17T01:52:00Z] [info] Refactored controllers: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC\n[2026-03-17T01:53:00Z] [info] Migrated StartupInitializer: Quarkus event -> ApplicationRunner\n[2026-03-17T01:54:00Z] [info] Migrated templates: Qute -> Thymeleaf (2 files rewritten, 2 removed)\n[2026-03-17T01:54:30Z] [info] Moved CSS to static/ directory\n[2026-03-17T01:55:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile CMD for Spring Boot JAR\n[2026-03-17T01:55:15Z] [info] Docker image built successfully\n[2026-03-17T01:55:27Z] [info] Application started in 6.454 seconds, seed data initialized\n[2026-03-17T01:56:00Z] [info] All 7 smoke tests PASSED\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors, 0 warnings\n- **Critical 